      <title>孟加拉国随着利率提高而引入塔卡爬行挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/bangladesh-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国央行引入了当地货币的爬行钉住制度，以保持塔卡稳定，并提高了关键利率以抑制通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/bangladesh-raises-key-policy-rate-to-tame-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:15:33 GMT</pubDate>
